        <ul class="usage-list">
          <li>Free endpoints require no authentication. V2 endpoints require an API key.</li>
          <li>All JSON endpoints return <code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *</code> for browser use.</li>
          <li>V1 endpoints enforce a rate limit of 100 requests per minute per IP.</li>
          <li>V2 endpoints use per-key daily limits: 100/day (free), 10,000/day (pro), unlimited (enterprise).</li>
          <li>V2 responses are never CDN-cached &mdash; always reflect live data.</li>
          <li>Data updates daily. Scores reflect the latest crawl.</li>
          <li>Tool IDs use <code>owner--repo</code> format (replace <code>/</code> with <code>--</code>).</li>
